{"tid":1301403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺69後一連串社運，好似創業咁？","createTime":"2019-07-09T15:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T00:40:58.000Z","uid":123335,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"111803316b0f6b07121c69fc7fd1fa5f57d157c4","tid":1301403,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:37:42.000Z","msg":"創出左好多新野出黎，前所未見：<br />\nEg 長輩圖文宣、冇大台 冇 Leader 既大型抗議示威遊行方式、G20前眾籌登外國報章、和理非同勇武派不割蓆  ..... 等 <br />\n<br />\n成件事亦好需要冒險精神(Risk taking) <br />\n名副其實 Go big or go home <br />\n好多勇士甚至為此賭上個人前途<br />\n冒上受刑事檢控風險企係最前線 <br />\n<br />\n唔似打工咁<br />\n所有付出都冇得guarantee 任何成果、收益 <br />\n冇人知個結果會係點 <br />\n大家只能摸黑咁一步步前進<br />\n咩都試試先囉<br />\n唔試過點知？<br />\n<br />\n成日話香港創業已死<br />\n我就唔係咁睇 <br />\n成班後生仔根本就係 entrepreneurs"},{"pid":"83e990fdc01dc054c23d66b3db28258c2f638be0","tid":1301403,"uid":69753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:38:28.000Z","msg":"<code>7.10前 - 一人一信反DQ - Link 1</code><br />\n<code>7.10 - 19:00~22:30 - 麥小姐追思會 ＠ 中環愛丁堡廣場🕊️</code><br />\n<code>7.11 - 14:00~22:00 - 梁烈士公眾告別禮 ＠ 渣華道遊樂場🕊️</code><br />\n<code>7.11 -  油尖旺區議會夢遊 - Link 2</code><br />\n<code>7.13 - 15:30 - 光復上水 ＠ 上水花園第一號</code><br />\n<code>7.14 - 沙田區大遊行 - Link 3</code><br />\n<code>7.27 - 紅磡土瓜灣遊行</code><br />\n<code>7.28 - 將軍澳遊行 - Link 4</code><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><em>Link 1: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/stopDQnow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FstopDQnow&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=c1899b11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/stopDQnow</a> / Link 2: <a href=\"http://t.me/ytm_dc711\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fytm_dc711&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=d6453395\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/ytm_dc711</a> / Link 3: <a href=\"https://t.me/st7142019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fst7142019&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBIeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=8020f